@startmindmap
title UTS_APB - Rancangan Desain Aplikasi (Mind Map)

* **UTS APB**
  * 🏗️ ARSITEKTUR UI
    * Entry Point
      * MyApp (MaterialApp)
      * Theme: Dark Mode
      * Home: HomePage
    * Page Navigation Hub
      * HomePage (Stateful)
        * AppBar dengan 2 Action
        * 7 Content Sections
      * Detail Pages (Stateful)
        * DetailPCPage
        * OrderFoodPage
      * Display Pages (Stateless)
        * ProfilePage
        * CartPage
        * BalancePage
        * PromoPage
    * State Management
      * Cart (Singleton)
        * items: List<CartItem>
        * totalNotifier: ValueNotifier
      * Page State
        * HomePage: ValueListener
        * DetailPCPage: selectedPC, hours, promo
        * OrderFoodPage: Map quantities

  * 🌳 WIDGET TREE
    * HomePage Structure
      * Scaffold
        * AppBar
          * leading: Balance Button
          * actions: Cart Total (ValueListenableBuilder)
        * Body: SingleChildScrollView
          * Section 1: Welcome Banner
          * Section 2: Promo Banner
          * Section 3: Menu Grid (2x2)
            * Pilih PC → DetailPCPage
            * Snack → OrderFoodPage
            * Profil → ProfilePage
            * Bantuan
          * Section 4: Info Features (3x)
          * Section 5: Spacing
    * DetailPCPage Structure
      * Scaffold
        * Header (Gradient Purple)
        * PC Options (Column)
          * PC Basic (Image + Info)
          * PC Pro (Image + Info)
          * PC Ultra (Image + Info)
        * If Selected Show:
          * Duration Slider (1-10 jam)
          * Promo Code TextField
          * Add to Cart Button
    * OrderFoodPage Structure
      * Scaffold
        * Header (Gradient Orange)
        * Food GridView (2x2)
          * Indomie Spesial (Image + Counter + Order)
          * Nasi Goreng (Image + Counter + Order)
          * Ayam Bakar (Image + Counter + Order)
          * Es Teh (Image + Counter + Order)
    * CartPage Structure
      * Scaffold
        * Empty Check
          * If empty: Empty State Message
          * If full: List Items
        * Cart Items ListView
          * Card × N Items
          * Name + Price + Qty + Subtotal
        * Bottom Section
          * Total Display
          * Checkout Button
    * ProfilePage Structure
      * Scaffold
        * Header Card (Cyan Gradient)
          * CircleAvatar (member_avatar.png)
          * Name & Email
          * Level & Points
        * Options Grid (2x3)
          * Login, Register, Edit Profil
          * Riwayat, Pengaturan, Logout
    * BalancePage Structure
      * Scaffold
        * Balance Card (Gradient)
          * Saldo: Rp 100.000
          * Top Up Button
        * History List
          * 4 Example Transactions
          * Title + Date + Amount

  * 🎨 PRINSIP LAYOUTING
    * Dark Mode Design
      * Background: #121212
      * Cards: #1E1E26
      * Accent: #00FFFF (Cyan)
      * Text Primary: #FFFFFF
      * Text Secondary: #FFFFFF70
    * Gradient Styling
      * Purple (PC): purpleAccent → blueAccent
      * Orange (Food): orangeAccent → redAccent
      * Cyan (Profile): cyanAccent → blueAccent
      * Direction: Top-Left to Bottom-Right
    * Responsive Grid
      * Home Menu: GridView 2x2
        * crossAxisCount: 2
        * spacing: 10
      * Profile Options: GridView 2x3
      * Food Items: GridView 2x2
      * Shrinkwrap: true
      * Physics: NeverScroll
    * Spacing System
      * Horizontal Padding: 16px
      * Vertical Margin: 10-20px
      * Card Margin: 16px all
      * Border Radius: 15px
      * Header Radius: 20px
      * Image Radius: 10px
    * Card & Container
      * Border Radius: 15px
      * Box Shadow: black26, blur 5
      * Normal: #1E1E26 bg
      * Selected: Cyan + border
      * Hover: Cyan opacity 0.2
    * Typography
      * Headline: 24px Bold
      * Title: 18px Bold
      * Subtitle: 16px Normal
      * Caption: 14px Normal
      * Small: 12px Normal
    * Interactive Elements
      * Button
        * bg: cyanAccent
        * text: black
        * padding: h50 v15
        * radius: 10px
      * TextField
        * fill: #2A2A3A
        * border: cyan 0.3 opacity
        * focused: cyan 2px
      * Slider
        * activeColor: cyan
        * min-max: 1-10
      * Notifications
        * SnackBar: 2 seconds

  * 🧭 ALUR NAVIGASI
    * Navigation Flow
      * MyApp
        * → HomePage (Initial)
      * HomePage (Hub)
        * AppBar.leading → BalancePage
        * AppBar.actions → CartPage
        * Menu[0] → DetailPCPage
        * Menu[1] → OrderFoodPage
        * Menu[2] → ProfilePage
        * Menu[3] → Placeholder
        * Promo → PromoPage
    * Navigation Method
      * Navigator.push()
      * MaterialPageRoute
      * All pages return with pop()
    * Cart Integration
      * DetailPCPage
        * Add Item → Cart.addItem()
        * Show SnackBar (2s)
      * OrderFoodPage
        * Pesan → Cart.addItem()
        * Show SnackBar (2s)
      * CartPage
        * Checkout → Cart.clear()
        * Show Success (2s)
        * pop() → HomePage

  * 🔄 STATE MANAGEMENT
    * Cart Singleton
      * Properties
        * items: List<CartItem>
        * totalNotifier: ValueNotifier<int>
      * Methods
        * addItem(name, price, qty)
          * Check existing item
          * Update qty or add new
          * Update notifier
        * getTotal(): int
          * Sum all prices × quantities
        * clear()
          * Clear items list
          * Reset notifier to 0
    * Page States
      * HomePage
        * Type: StatefulWidget
        * Listen: Cart.totalNotifier
        * Update: Keranjang AppBar
        * Builder: ValueListenableBuilder
      * DetailPCPage
        * Type: StatefulWidget
        * State: selectedPC, hours, promo
        * Action: addItem on button
      * OrderFoodPage
        * Type: StatefulWidget
        * State: Map<String, int> quantities
        * Action: addItem on Pesan
      * Other Pages
        * Type: StatelessWidget
        * No local state

  * 🎯 DESIGN SYSTEM
    * Color Palette
      * Primary Dark: #121212
      * Secondary Dark: #1E1E26
      * Accent: #00FFFF
      * Success: #4CAF50
      * Warning: #FF9800
      * Error: #F44336
      * Highlight: #9C27B0
    * Typography
      * Font Family: Default Material
      * Sizes: 12, 14, 16, 18, 24
      * Weights: 400, 500, 700
      * Line Height: 1.5
    * Components
      * Scaffold
        * bg: #121212
        * elevation: 0
      * AppBar
        * transparent
        * no elevation
        * custom leading/actions
      * Container
        * gradient + shadow
        * border-radius: 15px
      * GridView
        * responsive 2-column
        * auto spacing
      * Button
        * elevated + cyan
        * high contrast
      * TextField
        * dark + cyan border
        * rounded corners
      * Image
        * Image.asset()
        * rounded corners
        * BoxFit.cover
      * Avatar
        * CircleAvatar
        * AssetImage bg
    * Spacing
      * xs: 4px
      * s: 8px
      * m: 16px
      * l: 20px
      * xl: 24px
      * Consistent throughout
    * Shadows
      * Color: black26
      * Blur: 5px
      * Offset: (0, 2)
      * Applied to cards

@endmindmap
